{"id": 2345, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今，你觉得一场“真正放松的旅行”中哪些要素是必需的？", "description": "被工作压榨的现代人好不容易有次机会度假，假期的打开方式也变了。（题图来自：视觉中国 ©️ Ikon Images）", "record_count": 28748, "comment_count": 36, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180515163521XqdIspxoT2KukGLz.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-05-15T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4175, "title": "现如今，你觉得一场“真正放松的旅行”中哪些要素是必需的？", "content": "为了获得一场真正放松的旅行，你觉得哪些要素都是必须的？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 281955, "content": "不带电脑，实在临时需要工作向酒店or工作人员借", "image": "img/option/option/20180515161818G0Rr79kzmpA8gPuT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 281956, "content": "酒店一定要床舒服，贵点都行", "image": "img/option/option/20180515161923lYjXKDV9ukh20zUw.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 281957, "content": "行程中绝不出现早上九点之前就得出发的项目", "image": "img/option/option/20180515163607eYl6mJDz3dP2VAr8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 281958, "content": "有地陪或包车，随便看点攻略就能上", "image": "img/option/option/20180515163702yxXFMeIoHPLg96VJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 281959, "content": "出门前连续加班一周，处理掉手头和可能将有的活", "image": "img/option/option/20180515163327niUVOuhgWvRZGp4A.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 281963, "content": "圆满解决“休假时手里各种工作交给谁处理”", "image": "img/option/option/201805151635041xzOfNhVkCTgnvbI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 281964, "content": "挑没太多游客的城市、避开热门景点", "image": "img/option/option/20180515162119r6QJxunsNXpDHGTb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 281977, "content": "社交斋戒，不发朋友圈不刷微博", "image": "img/option/option/20180515163152qeJd0pZGY8LPrKuV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 282005, "content": "没有代购预约", "image": "img/option/option/20180515170825FxdWHr0vqJSn5ePB.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 282006, "content": "一个合拍的旅伴", "image": "img/option/option/20180515180705EeK6tQnrNfdYmakL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 282007, "content": "不要旅伴，就我自己一个人", "image": "img/option/option/20180515171711TF5mc8kjIM4QOHBW.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 282008, "content": "吃东西很随意，不用排队预约网红店", "image": "img/option/option/20180515172305Zm1s5KRXEUxaBCMg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 282009, "content": "有大量泡温泉躺沙滩时间，微信步数平均不到一万/天", "image": "img/option/option/20180515172455uVMqrl5P3ibWTY02.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}